---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import BtnLink from "../components/shared/BtnLink.astro"
---

<Layout title="Bine ati venit le Cursuri SEO.">
  <section class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-900">
    <div class="py-8 lg:py-16 px-4 mx-auto max-w-screen-md">
      <h2
        class="mb-4 text-4xl tracking-tight font-extrabold text-center text-gray-900 dark:text-white"
      >
        Contactati-ne
      </h2>
      <p
        class="mb-8 lg:mb-16 font-light text-center text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 sm:text-xl"
      >
        Scrieti-ne la office@cursuri-seo.ro sau sunati la 0764 118 196 pentru a
        intra in legatura cu noi, de luni pana vineri intre orele 11:00 - 19:00,
        si in weekend intre orele 10:00 - 14:00.
      </p>
      <p
        class="mb-8 lg:mb-16 font-light text-center text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 sm:text-xl"
      >
        Pentru inscrierea la cursuri va rugam sa completati formularul de
        inscriere rapida de mai jos:
      </p>
      <form action="#" class="space-y-8">
        <div class="flex flex-row flex-wrap ">
          <div class="flex flex-col p-2 w-1/2">
            <p class=" text-gray-700 dark:text-white">Vreau sa particip la cursul:</p>
            <label class="inline-flex items-center mt-3">
              <input
                type="checkbox"
                class="form-checkbox h-5 w-5 text-gray-600"
                
              /><span class="ml-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-white">SEO practic 23-24 sep 1200 lei</span>
            </label>

            <label class="inline-flex items-center mt-3">
              <input
                type="checkbox"
                class="form-checkbox h-5 w-5 text-red-600"
                
              /><span class="ml-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-white">SM&FB Ads 30sep-1oct 1200 lei</span>
            </label>

            <label class="inline-flex items-center mt-3">
              <input
                type="checkbox"
                class="form-checkbox h-5 w-5 text-orange-600"
                
              /><span class="ml-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-white">Google Ads 21-22 oct 1200 lei</span>
            </label>

            <label class="inline-flex items-center mt-3">
              <input
                type="checkbox"
                class="form-checkbox h-5 w-5 text-yellow-600"
                
              /><span class="ml-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-white">Content Writing 28-29 oct 900 lei</span>
            </label>

            <label class="inline-flex items-center mt-3">
              <input
                type="checkbox"
                class="form-checkbox h-5 w-5 text-green-600"
                
              /><span class="ml-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-white">Google Analytics 18-19 nov 1200 lei</span>
            </label>

            <label class="inline-flex items-center mt-3">
              <input
                type="checkbox"
                class="form-checkbox h-5 w-5 text-teal-600"
                
              /><span class="ml-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-white">Marketing Online 16-17 dec 1200 lei</span>
            </label>

            <label class="inline-flex items-center mt-3">
              <input
                type="checkbox"
                class="form-checkbox h-5 w-5 text-blue-600"
                
              /><span class="ml-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-white">Training 1 la 1 online 240 lei/â€‹ora</span>
            </label>

            <label class="inline-flex items-center mt-3">
              <input
                type="checkbox"
                class="form-checkbox h-5 w-5 text-indigo-600"
                
              /><span class="ml-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-white">MAKE IT ACADEMY online 3800 lei</span>
            </label>

            <p class="mt-4 text-gray-700 dark:text-white">Mod de participare:</p>

            <label class="inline-flex items-center mt-3">
                <input
                  type="checkbox"
                  class="form-checkbox h-5 w-5 text-blue-600"
                  
                /><span class="ml-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-white">Online</span>
              </label>
  
              <label class="inline-flex items-center mt-3">
                <input
                  type="checkbox"
                  class="form-checkbox h-5 w-5 text-indigo-600"
                  
                /><span class="ml-2 text-gray-700 dark:text-white">La sediu</span>
              </label>
          </div>

          <div class="flex flex-col w-1/2">
            <div>
              <label
                for="email"
                class="block my-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-300"
                >Email</label
              >
              <input
                type="email"
                id="email"
                class="shadow-sm bg-gray-50 border border-gray-300 text-gray-900 text-sm rounded-lg focus:ring-primary-500 focus:border-primary-500 block w-full p-2.5 dark:bg-gray-700 dark:border-gray-600 dark:placeholder-gray-400 dark:text-white dark:focus:ring-primary-500 dark:focus:border-primary-500 dark:shadow-sm-light"

                required
              />
            </div>
            <div>
              <label
                for="subject"
                class="block my-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-300"
                >Telefon</label
              >
              <input
                type="text"
                id="subject"
                class="block p-3 w-full text-sm text-gray-900 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg border border-gray-300 shadow-sm focus:ring-primary-500 focus:border-primary-500 dark:bg-gray-700 dark:border-gray-600 dark:placeholder-gray-400 dark:text-white dark:focus:ring-primary-500 dark:focus:border-primary-500 dark:shadow-sm-light"

                required
              />
            </div>
            <div>
                <label
                  for="email"
                  class="block my-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-300"
                  >Nume sau date firma</label
                >
                <input
                  type="email"
                  id="email"
                  class="shadow-sm bg-gray-50 border border-gray-300 text-gray-900 text-sm rounded-lg focus:ring-primary-500 focus:border-primary-500 block w-full p-2.5 dark:bg-gray-700 dark:border-gray-600 dark:placeholder-gray-400 dark:text-white dark:focus:ring-primary-500 dark:focus:border-primary-500 dark:shadow-sm-light"

                  required
                />
              </div>
              <div>
                <label
                  for="subject"
                  class="block my-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-300"
                  >CNP</label
                >
                <input
                  type="text"
                  id="subject"
                  class="block p-3 w-full text-sm text-gray-900 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg border border-gray-300 shadow-sm focus:ring-primary-500 focus:border-primary-500 dark:bg-gray-700 dark:border-gray-600 dark:placeholder-gray-400 dark:text-white dark:focus:ring-primary-500 dark:focus:border-primary-500 dark:shadow-sm-light"

                  required
                />
              </div>
              <div>
                <label
                  for="subject"
                  class="block my-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-300"
                  >Adresa</label
                >
                <input
                  type="text"
                  id="subject"
                  class="block p-3 w-full text-sm text-gray-900 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg border border-gray-300 shadow-sm focus:ring-primary-500 focus:border-primary-500 dark:bg-gray-700 dark:border-gray-600 dark:placeholder-gray-400 dark:text-white dark:focus:ring-primary-500 dark:focus:border-primary-500 dark:shadow-sm-light"

                  required
                />
              </div>
            <div class="sm:col-span-2">
              <label
                for="message"
                class="block my-2 text-sm font-medium text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-400"
                >Mesaj optional</label
              >
              <textarea
                id="message"
                rows="6"
                class="block p-2.5 w-full text-sm text-gray-900 bg-gray-50 rounded-lg shadow-sm border border-gray-300 focus:ring-primary-500 focus:border-primary-500 dark:bg-gray-700 dark:border-gray-600 dark:placeholder-gray-400 dark:text-white dark:focus:ring-primary-500 dark:focus:border-primary-500"
              ></textarea>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="lg:min-w-max flex items-center sm:w-max w-full pb-6 lg:pb-0 border-b border-box-bg lg:border-0 px-6 lg:px-0">
            <BtnLink text="Inscrieti-va" href="contact" className="flex justify-center w-full sm:w-max" variant="primary"/>
        </div>
      </form>
      <p
        class="mt-8 lg:mb-16 font-light text-center text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 sm:text-xl"
      >
      Toate detaliile privind cursurile sunt trimise prin agenda cursului spre cei pe care ii asteptam sa participe.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
